headline: Auxiliary Requests Refused Due To UPC's Strict Added Matter Requirements
summary: In the latest decision in the DexCom vs Abbott saga at the UPC, the Paris Local Division refused DexCom's three auxiliary requests to amend on the ground of added matter. The decision sheds further...
